snippet.title: Life in Bunker
snippet.description:
Release Date: 25 Feb? 2016
 
Life in Bunker - is a bunker-building simulator. Where you, as the bunker Warden, control a group of residents, expand the bunker, and do your best to last long enough, until the surface becomes habitable.

http://lifeinbunker.com
